  "prompt": "A good friend of mine is gay , but we made out before telling me. Is there any chance he is bisexual ?",
  "response": "It's certainly possible that your friend may be bisexual. Sexual orientation can be complex and fluid for some people, and individuals may not always fit neatly into one category. Making out with you before telling you he is gay could indicate that he has attractions to more than one gender, or it could be a one-time experience driven by other factors, like curiosity or experimentation. The best way to understand his feelings and orientation is to have an open and honest conversation directly with him. Respect his response and give him space to share how he genuinely feels.",
